criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

  -  Diagnosis of progressive keratoconus

Exclusion Criteria:

  -  Anterior corneal curvature steeper than 61 D;

  -  central corneal thickness <400 um

  -  corneal scarring;

  -  descemetocele;

  -  history of herpetic keratitis;

  -  Concomitant eye diseases;

  -  Inflammatory eye diseases;

  -  Glaucoma;

  -  Cataract;

  -  Pregnancy
